name: Cinnamon Cake
comment: Cinnamon comes from bark. So how does it taste so good?

name: Dundee Cake
comment: The ultimate accompaniment for a cup of tea

name: Cheesecake
comment: Rich and creamy, perhaps one of the most decadent desserts?

name: Bundt Cake
comment: I'd not heard of this one. Every day's a school day. I'm guessing it has pistachio.

name: Pumpkin Pie
comment: Can a pie be a cake? I guess so. Great for halloween, this one.

name: Honey Cake
comment: Bees - very important. Anything with honey is always good.

name: Lime Cake
comment: A lime is like a slightly politer lemon. Less acerbic, and yet just as flavourful. No offense, lemons.
